title: The Bargain v01 (2014) (Digital) (DR & Quinch-Empire).cbr
description:
The Bargain v01 (2014) (Digital) (DR & Quinch-Empire)


With only days left to break a pact for his soul, Jackson Connolly attempts one final, desperate gamble at salvation. It's a journey that will take him from the backwoods of ghostly Louisiana to the seductive lights of a 1950s New Orleans burlesque club. Adventure and moody noir fuse in this supernatural tale of ghosts, hellhounds and hoodoo magic
